{"tid":675980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」吖嫲 一路好走","createTime":"2018-05-24T04:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T11:01:13.000Z","uid":31104,"like":4,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6a82a659b365205bdc662e7b96d1da75280679cf","tid":675980,"uid":31104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:11:04.000Z","msg":"繼「懷念爺爺系列」之後<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/115837_725da8576020770ee31237d6a8387e60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F115837_725da8576020770ee31237d6a8387e60.png&h=410ba2e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條撚樣都好有孝心<br />\n趁你嫲嫲死唔斷氣迴光返照時 不忘大合照懷念一下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/115502_917a39fce9eb9753ace2a2e391aadd05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F115502_917a39fce9eb9753ace2a2e391aadd05.png&h=2bd97f6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/115503_cace045002b51d1154437a1295d77a2c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F115503_cace045002b51d1154437a1295d77a2c.png&h=b713c7d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇錯 人最緊要向前望 你睇下幾快笑番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/120911_c8a2308ee34555fd2c54b4a695f1a5f3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F120911_c8a2308ee34555fd2c54b4a695f1a5f3.png&h=8adea0a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係對自己排骨好有自信？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/115511_369c4a287eb3570e77146e91165cf722.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F115511_369c4a287eb3570e77146e91165cf722.png&h=17d34f28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n極度懷疑呢條友係智障仔 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/115515_deea24e30c83660c2c19d82f655015ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F115515_deea24e30c83660c2c19d82f655015ae.png&h=7be2e00e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/115517_1ec2bea4a2a8117f2f563cc1ef0b953e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F115517_1ec2bea4a2a8117f2f563cc1ef0b953e.png&h=95d62f94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n試吓唔好睇棚馬牙 佢地大家都有幾分相似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/120617_4016463a067fb341819cd523d593d021.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F120617_4016463a067fb341819cd523d593d021.png&h=c06867fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nto be continued ...."},{"pid":"49265ea91de84bb5ebe295bff27ce1408e128cee","tid":675980,"uid":31104,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/121531_c36c435550620d70fb91c6c34dfc1eb7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F121531_c36c435550620d70fb91c6c34dfc1eb7.png&h=fef8d3f2&s={SIZE}\" />依家啲00後真係呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90628737537c7b267a4e96326e5373d4488b8a0","tid":675980,"uid":58140,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:16:55.000Z","msg":"試下張死人圖加密<b